channel.title: Kilop-Scape - A Better Delta -- OVER 1 DOWNLOAD
channel.description:
[center][u][b]Information & Links:[/b][/u][/center] I'm releasing this project as I have permission from Kilop to do so, and that this is no longer running. Please do not flame because it's a Delta; we made this over 3 years ago.
Kilop-Scape was a pretty successful server, it got up to about 100 players. But then we dropped in player amounts and got 50-70 on; usually in the 60s. Then we opened a second server; named it Kilop-PvP, which pulled away players from the 317 server. And then we had about 20 on the 317, and 50-60 on Kilop-PvP.
Kilop hired me as one of her programmers and I did 75% of the coding, but the server was named after her; it was her project, she started it. It was only me and her programming the server, and when I say that I did 75% of the work, well here's what I did:
[ul][li]Made the website[/li] [li]Coded the client[/li] [li]Coded over 62% of the server.[/li][/ul]
Here what Kilop did:
[ul][li]Coded 38% of the server[/li][/ul]
So, I did more work then she did obviously.
[center]Source: http://www.mediafire.com/?kx0v1incfd4gptf Client: http://www.mediafire.com/?ceb05dhkdt5m9bq[/center] [hr] [center][u][b]Server Content:[/b][/u][/center]
[ol][li]100% working godsword stances[/li] [li]God Wars[/li] [li]Pest Control - 70% done[/li] [li]Barrows[/li] [li]Corpral Beast[/li] [li]Duel Arena[/li] [li]Donor ranks & zone[/li] [li]Over 20 commands all working[/li] [li]Decently stable[/li] [li]Giant Mole[/li] [li]All skills work (not 100%)[/li] [li]Home training[/li] [li]Barbarian Village[/li] [li]Donor shop[/li] [li]Falador[/li] [li]Slayer Tower[/li] [li]King Black Dragon[/li] [li]General Graardor[/li] [li]Kalphite Queen[/li] [li]Around 7 shops(if I remember correctly)[/li] [li]Fun PK[/li] [li]Dragon claws[/li] [li]A different home than Edgeville[/li] [li]Mithril Dragons[/li] [li]Edited hits[/li] [li]Better combat system[/li][/ol]
